704
00:42:50,640 --> 00:42:54,079
There's nothing wrong with requests, but it's not a boundary.

705
00:42:54,079 --> 00:42:59,119
Because if you're setting what you call a boundary and you're really making a request,

706
00:42:59,119 --> 00:43:07,119
you're giving all of your power away to the other person because you're saying the success of this important moment depends on my 2-year-old.

707
00:43:07,119 --> 00:43:07,839
What?

708
00:43:07,839 --> 00:43:10,240
I'm not going to I'm not going to give my power to my 2-year-old.

709
00:43:10,240 --> 00:43:13,920
And I always tell parents, I would bet on you any day over your kid.

710
00:43:13,920 --> 00:43:15,119
And it's not cuz I don't like your kid.

711
00:43:15,119 --> 00:43:16,079
I do like your kid.

712
00:43:16,079 --> 00:43:17,839
I just believe in you more.

