00:51:20,160 --> 00:51:22,400
That's what I need because I have a lot of strong ideas.

848
00:51:22,400 --> 00:51:26,160
So, I love people who push back and have a POV.

849
00:51:26,160 --> 00:51:29,599
And I think especially at work when there's so much going on, right?

850
00:51:29,599 --> 00:51:31,119
It could be so stressful.

851
00:51:31,119 --> 00:51:36,800
Having a leader you can locate, which means I have a POV to be able to say, "This might not be what you want.

852
00:51:36,800 --> 00:51:41,440
I believe this is the best decision and I believe we're a strong enough team to work toward that."

